qDef.qDef:
Pick(
$(v_Selected_Measure_MT_KG)
,pick([%SynHeadersOne_EMC]
	,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
	,
    (
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    	+
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
    )
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])
	,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID_Minus1)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])	
	,
    (
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
      	-Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    )	
	,
    (
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
      	-Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])
    )
    ,
    (
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])
        -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    )
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        ,$(v_Quotations_Created_MT_CM)
    ,$(v_Quotations_Sent_MT_CM)
    ,$(v_Pending_Order_MT_CY)
)

,pick([%SynHeadersOne_EMC]

    	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Kg])
      	-Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Kg])
    )	
	,

    	+Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Kg])

        -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Kg])
    )
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Kg])
     ,$(v_Quotations_Created_MT_CM) *1000

))
